@undeadequipped talked me into working with him on a list of prompts for May. If you were around last year, this was a lot of fun. I definitely made new “art” buddies and we collectively made a bunch of really dumb art. 

There are no real rules but if you wanna participate, use the #30daysofcritters so we can see and share some of your drawings. 

Thanks to everyone who made suggestions for the list. Some of those definitely made it in.

Oh, one last thing. Every drawing we make this year is going to go in our @threadless shops. We’ve both been neglecting them and wanna satisfy all of the “this should be on a shirt” comments 🙇🏻
